My given name is Motonari!"},{"lineNumber":226429,"originalJapaneseLine":"　怪力悪童とはオレのことよ！」","translatedEnglishLine":"The strong-armed wild child, that's me!\""},

{"lineNumber":226430,"originalJapaneseLine":"ギラギラと敵意を湛えた瞳は、","translatedEnglishLine":"His eyes gleamed fiercely with hostility,"},

{"lineNumber":226431,"originalJapaneseLine":"せわしなく動き回っていた。","translatedEnglishLine":"restlessly moving about."},

{"lineNumber":226432,"originalJapaneseLine":"まるで次なる獲物を探すように。","translatedEnglishLine":"As if searching for his next prey."},

{"lineNumber":226433,"originalJapaneseLine":"「で、こんな所をゾロゾロと何用だ？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"So, what brings a bunch of you here, anyway?\""}, 

{"lineNumber":226434,"originalJapaneseLine":"「お姉ちゃん達は今、","translatedEnglishLine":"\"The older sisters are currently,"},

{"lineNumber":226435,"originalJapaneseLine":"　魔王ランスを倒す旅の最中なの」","translatedEnglishLine":"on a journey to defeat the Demon King Rance.\""}, 

{"lineNumber":226436,"originalJapaneseLine":"「良かったら、","translatedEnglishLine":"\"If you like,"},

{"lineNumber":226437,"originalJapaneseLine":"　元就ちゃんも来てくれないかな？」","translatedEnglishLine":"would you join us too, Motonari-chan?\""}, 

{"lineNumber":226438,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ククク、なるほどな……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Heh heh heh, I see...\""}, 

{"lineNumber":226439,"originalJapaneseLine":"「断る！！！！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"I refuse!!!!\""}, 

{"lineNumber":226440,"originalJapaneseLine":"「強敵との戦いは毛利の本懐だが、","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Battling strong enemies is the true desire of the Mouri,"},

{"lineNumber":226441,"originalJapaneseLine":"　人に言われて戦うなどまっぴらよ」","translatedEnglishLine":"but fighting just because someone tells me to is out of the question.\""}, 

{"lineNumber":226442,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ザンスと似たようなこと言って……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"You're saying something similar to Zansu...\""}, 

{"lineNumber":226443,"originalJapaneseLine":"「アア？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Huh?\""}, 

{"lineNumber":226444,"originalJapaneseLine":"「うう……どうしても駄目？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Ugh... it's really no good?\""}, 

{"lineNumber":226445,"originalJapaneseLine":"「駄目だ！！！！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"No way!!!!\""}, 

{"lineNumber":226446,"originalJapaneseLine":"「おお……","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Oh..."}, 

{"lineNumber":226447,"originalJapaneseLine":"　リセットさんの言うことも聞かないんだ……」","translatedEnglishLine":"You won't even listen to Reset's words...\""}, 

{"lineNumber":226448,"originalJapaneseLine":"「もっちゃん……","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Mocchan..."}, 

{"lineNumber":226449,"originalJapaneseLine":"　魔王の子一の暴れん坊だから……」","translatedEnglishLine":"You're the most reckless of the Demon King's children...\""}, 

{"lineNumber":226450,"originalJapaneseLine":"「合理的じゃない分、","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Because you're not rational,"}, 

{"lineNumber":226451,"originalJapaneseLine":"　ザンスよりもコントロールは難しいかもね」","translatedEnglishLine":"you might be harder to control than Zansu.\""}, 

{"lineNumber":226452,"originalJapaneseLine":"「カカカ……","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Kakaka..."}, 

{"lineNumber":226453,"originalJapaneseLine":"　オレをどうしても連れていくってんなら……」","translatedEnglishLine":"If you insist on taking me along..."}, 

{"lineNumber":226454,"originalJapaneseLine":"「力ずくで来い！」","translatedEnglishLine":"Come by force!\""}, 

{"lineNumber":226455,"originalJapaneseLine":"「その場合、お前ら全員オレの敵！","translatedEnglishLine":"\"In that case, you all become my enemies!"}, 

{"lineNumber":226456,"originalJapaneseLine":"　この場で即刻皆殺しだ！」","translatedEnglishLine":"I'll kill you all here immediately!\""}, 

{"lineNumber":226457,"originalJapaneseLine":"身の丈以上もある巨大な刀で、","translatedEnglishLine":"With a huge blade taller than himself,"}, 

{"lineNumber":226458,"originalJapaneseLine":"ズドンと地を揺らした。","translatedEnglishLine":"he struck the ground with a thunderous impact."}, 

{"lineNumber":226459,"originalJapaneseLine":"「もー、元就ちゃんはすぐに","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Geez, Motonari-chan is so quick to"}, 

{"lineNumber":226460,"originalJapaneseLine":"　周囲の人間を敵と味方に分けるー」","translatedEnglishLine":"divide people around him into enemies and allies—\""}, 

{"lineNumber":226461,"originalJapaneseLine":"「黙れ！　リセット！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Silence! Reset!\""}, 

{"lineNumber":226462,"originalJapaneseLine":"「もう、お前の口八丁には乗らんぞ！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"I won't fall for your smooth talk anymore!\""}, 

{"lineNumber":226463,"originalJapaneseLine":"「さーっ、オレを連れて行くなら力ずくしかないぞ！","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Now, if you're taking me with you, force is the only way!"}, 

{"lineNumber":226464,"originalJapaneseLine":"　最初の相手は誰だ！　ザンスか乱義か！","translatedEnglishLine":"Who's the first opponent? Zansu or Rangy?!"}, 

{"lineNumber":226465,"originalJapaneseLine":"　ぐわっはははは！　二人同時でもいいぞ！」","translatedEnglishLine":"Gwahahaha! Taking on both at the same time is fine too!\""}, 

{"lineNumber":226466,"originalJapaneseLine":"さあ早く来い来いと、","translatedEnglishLine":"Come on, come on quickly,"}, 

{"lineNumber":226467,"originalJapaneseLine":"元就の瞳はギラギラと輝いて、","translatedEnglishLine":"Motonari's eyes glittered fiercely,"}, 

{"lineNumber":226468,"originalJapaneseLine":"殺し合いを楽しもうとしているのが伝わった。","translatedEnglishLine":"conveying that he was eager to enjoy a deadly fight."}, 

{"lineNumber":226469,"originalJapaneseLine":"「な、なんて危険な奴だ……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"W-what a dangerous guy...\""}, 

{"lineNumber":226470,"originalJapaneseLine":"「これなら偉そうなだけな分、","translatedEnglishLine":"\"If that's the case, the arrogant one might be better,"}, 

{"lineNumber":226471,"originalJapaneseLine":"　ザンスの方がマシかも……」","translatedEnglishLine":"Zansu could be preferable...\""}, 

{"lineNumber":226472,"originalJapaneseLine":"「しばくぞ、テメェ」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"I'll beat you up, you bastard!\""}, 

{"lineNumber":226473,"originalJapaneseLine":"「で、おい。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"So, hey."}, 

{"lineNumber":226474,"originalJapaneseLine":"　リーダーである＜エール＞は、","translatedEnglishLine":"The leader, <Eiru>,"}, 

{"lineNumber":226475,"originalJapaneseLine":"　どうすんだ？」","translatedEnglishLine":"what are you going to do?\""}, 

{"lineNumber":226476,"originalJapaneseLine":"「お、おお、そうだな！","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Y-yeah, that's right!"}, 

{"lineNumber":226477,"originalJapaneseLine":"　＜エール＞、どうする！？」","translatedEnglishLine":"<Eiru>, what will you do!?\""}, 

{"lineNumber":226478,"originalJapaneseLine":"「はい。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Yes."}, 

{"lineNumber":226479,"originalJapaneseLine":"　ちょっと待ちなさい」","translatedEnglishLine":"Please wait a moment.\""}, 

{"lineNumber":226480,"originalJapaneseLine":"先手必勝とばかりに戦おうとしたあなたを、","translatedEnglishLine":"As you tried to strike first and win,"}, 

{"lineNumber":226481,"originalJapaneseLine":"乱義が引き留めた。","translatedEnglishLine":"Rangy stopped you."}]}

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あなた達は改めて元就に挨拶をしていた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You all greeted Motonari once again.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「はい、それじゃ＜エール＞ちゃん。
改めて紹介するね」
「毛利家の跡継ぎ、元就ちゃん」
「ほお……＜エール＞・モフス……
お前が魔王の子のリーダー、か……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: So you are the leader of the Demon King's children..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「性は毛利！　名は元就！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "My family name is Mouri! My given name is Motonari!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 怪力悪童とはオレのことよ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The strong-armed wild child, that's me!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ギラギラと敵意を湛えた瞳は、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: His eyes gleamed fiercely with hostility,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: せわしなく動き回っていた。
まるで次なる獲物を探すように。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: As if searching for his next prey.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「で、こんな所をゾロゾロと何用だ？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "So, what brings a bunch of you here, anyway?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「お姉ちゃん達は今、
魔王ランスを倒す旅の最中なの」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: on a journey to defeat the Demon King Rance."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「良かったら、
元就ちゃんも来てくれないかな？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: would you join us too, Motonari-chan?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ククク、なるほどな……」
「強敵との戦いは毛利の本懐だが、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Battling strong enemies is the true desire of the Mouri,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 人に言われて戦うなどまっぴらよ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: but fighting just because someone tells me to is out of the question."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ザンスと似たようなこと言って……」
「アア？」
「うう……どうしても駄目？」
「おお……
リセットさんの言うことも聞かないんだ……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You won't even listen to Reset's words..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「もっちゃん……
魔王の子一の暴れん坊だから……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You're the most reckless of the Demon King's children..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「合理的じゃない分、
ザンスよりもコントロールは難しいかもね」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: you might be harder to control than Zansu."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「カカカ……
オレをどうしても連れていくってんなら……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: If you insist on taking me along...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「力ずくで来い！」
「その場合、お前ら全員オレの敵！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "In that case, you all become my enemies!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: この場で即刻皆殺しだ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I'll kill you all here immediately!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 身の丈以上もある巨大な刀で、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: With a huge blade taller than himself,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ズドンと地を揺らした。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: he struck the ground with a thunderous impact.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「もー、元就ちゃんはすぐに
周囲の人間を敵と味方に分けるー」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: divide people around him into enemies and allies—"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「黙れ！　リセット！」
「もう、お前の口八丁には乗らんぞ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "I won't fall for your smooth talk anymore!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「さーっ、オレを連れて行くなら力ずくしかないぞ！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Now, if you're taking me with you, force is the only way!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 最初の相手は誰だ！　ザンスか乱義か！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Who's the first opponent? Zansu or Rangy?!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ぐわっはははは！　二人同時でもいいぞ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Gwahahaha! Taking on both at the same time is fine too!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: さあ早く来い来いと、
元就の瞳はギラギラと輝いて、
殺し合いを楽しもうとしているのが伝わった。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: conveying that he was eager to enjoy a deadly fight.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「な、なんて危険な奴だ……」
「これなら偉そうなだけな分、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "If that's the case, the arrogant one might be better,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ザンスの方がマシかも……」
「しばくぞ、テメェ」
「で、おい。
リーダーである＜エール＞は、
どうすんだ？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: what are you going to do?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「お、おお、そうだな！
＜エール＞、どうする！？」
「はい。
ちょっと待ちなさい」
先手必勝とばかりに戦おうとしたあなたを、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: As you tried to strike first and win,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 乱義が引き留めた。

translationLines.description: Array of objects, each representing a line from the input

originalJapaneseLine.description: The original line in Japanese exactly as it was in the input

translatedEnglishLine.description: The original line translated to English

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: divide people around him into enemies and allies—"

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: conveying that he was eager to enjoy a deadly fight.

先手必勝とばかりに戦おうとしたあなたを、
